Metracker

A guard for your database.

Capture metrics, limit connections, and protect your database from 
suspicious queries. That's what Metracker offers you.

Discover the repository:

./example/db - is a database example to be protect.

./build.bash - is a script to build the CLI.

./interceptor - is the heart of the Metracker, there is create the
interceptor for your database.